data.title: Generator Light Speed + Refract
data.description: When executing the A Site, entry out towards Generator as shown in the video and use your Refract when deemed necessary. You can also dash on top of Generator, however you will not have a smoke to cover you and Defenders may shoot you as you do so.

data.title: Boat Clear Light Speed + Refract
data.description: Aggressively dash out to Market with your Refract active to seek out a difficult fight for Defenders to take, as well as clearing important angles for your team to execute.
